<h2 style="text-align: center;">BYU-Idaho On-Campus Housing Payment Process</h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>What are some important things to consider when purchasing a contract?</strong></p>
<p>Students should carefully read the BYU-Idaho Student Landlord contract and be very familiar with the terms and conditions.&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>When is my rent due?</strong></p>
<p>Rent is charged in three equal amounts.&nbsp; Rent posts to the student's account at the beginning of the month and is due by the last day of the month.</p>
