<p><strong>How do I pay my rent?</strong></p>
<p>Rent is charged to your student account under Campus Housing.&nbsp; To make a payment please log into my.byui.edu and click on the finance tab.&nbsp;&nbsp; BYU-Idaho has multiple payment methods available to students.</p>
<p><a class="extLink" href="http://www.byui.edu/financial-services/my-account/payment-methods">http://www.byui.edu/financial-services/my-account/payment-methods</a></p>
<p><strong>Is a deposit required to purchase a contract?</strong></p>
<p>Yes, students will pay $100 when they purchase their contract.&nbsp; $75 will be used as a refundable deposit, and $25 will be used for a one time processing fee.&nbsp; Students who purchase additional contracts are not required to pay multiple deposits or processing fees.</p>
